        <h1>Welcome To ABC Retail</h1>

    <p1>Welcome to ABC Retail, where your shopping experience is our top priority! At ABC Retail, we’re more than just an online store; we’re a community dedicated to bringing 
        you a wide array of high-quality products that cater to your every need. From the latest fashion trends and cutting-edge electronics to essential home goods and unique 
        specialty items, we’ve carefully curated our collections to offer something for everyone. Our platform is designed with you in mind, providing a seamless, user-friendly
        interface that makes finding what you need easier than ever. We pride ourselves on delivering exceptional customer service, with a team always ready to assist you, 
        whether you have questions about a product or need help with your order. With secure payment options, fast shipping, and a commitment to excellence, ABC Retail is
        here to ensure that your online shopping experience is smooth, enjoyable, and satisfying. Discover the difference at ABC Retail, where quality meets convenience, and customer
        satisfaction is our guarantee. Happy shopping!
    </p1>

    <div id="imageBox1"><img src="~/images/ashim-d-silva-ZmgJiztRHXE-unsplash.jpg" width="750px" height="400px" /></div>

    <div id="indexBox1">Before You Start Shopping</div>
    <div id="indexBox2"> At ABC Retail, we’re committed to providing you with a personalized shopping experience that’s tailored to your preferences. 
        To ensure this, we require all our customers to log in before making a purchase. By logging in, you gain access to a range of exclusive features 
        designed to enhance your shopping journey. This includes the ability to save your favorite items for later, track your order history, and receive 
        personalized product recommendations based on your past purchases and browsing habits. Logging in also allows us to offer a more secure shopping environment, 
        protecting your personal information and payment details with the highest levels of encryption and security. Additionally, being logged in ensures a smoother 
        checkout process, with your saved information allowing for quick and easy transactions. While browsing our collections is always open to everyone, making a purchase 
        is a privilege reserved for registered users, ensuring that your shopping experience is both safe and seamless. So, take a moment to log in or create an account,
        and unlock the full potential of what ABC Retail has to offer.</div>

    
        


    <div id="indexBox3">Please Create A Profile</div>
    <div id="createUser">
        <form asp-action="AddCustomerProfile" method="post">
            <div id="userInputSpace">
                <label for="name">NAME:</label>
                <input type="text" name="FirstName" />
            </div>
            <div id="userInputSpace">
                <label for="name">SURNAME:</label>
                <input type="text" name="LastName" />
            </div>
            <div id="userInputSpace">
                <label for="name">E-MAIL:</label>
                <input type="email" name="Email" />
            </div>
            <div id="userInputSpace">
                <label for="name">PHONE-NUMBER:</label>
                <input type="text" name="PhoneNumber" />
            </div>
            <div id="userInputSpace">
            <button type="submit">Add Profile</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>


    </body>


